{"Body": "Harriet Burgess\n\nPolaiteoir\u044c na t\u044cre - nach bhfuil sibh br\u0436an den ghr\u0429pa lochtach seo, a chairde? T\u0440imse, gan dabht ar bith. Anois, t\u0440 \u0440r dTaoiseach nua againne\u0401 N\u044clim f\u0437s cinnte faoi. B\u045afh\u0436idir go bhfuil r\u0436 nua polait\u044cochta ag teacht, b\u045afh\u0436idir go mbeidh Fine Gael d\u044creach cos\u0429il leis na buachaill\u044c n\u0440ireacha as Fianna F\u0440il. N\u044cl fhios againn f\u0437s.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_2860\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\" caption=\"&quot;Is \u0436 mo thuairimse go bhfuil s\u0436 do theist ag an rialtas an Ghaeilge a chur chun chinn go l\u0440idir- ar an idirl\u044con.&quot;\"]<a href=\"http://www.universitytimes.ie/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/teen-computer.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-2860\" title=\"Boy working with laptop\" src=\"http://www.universitytimes.ie/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/teen-computer-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>[/caption]\n\nAch chomh fada is a bhaineann se liomsa, n\u044c deas an comhartha \u0436 an polasa\u044c at\u0440 ag \u2554anna \u041c Cionnaith maidir le st\u0440das na Gaeilge. T\u0440\u0430\u2554anna ag dearbh\u0429 go bhfuil s\u0436 mar aidhm aige an Ghaeilge a bheith roghnach mar \u0440bhar don Ardteist. An ag magadh at\u0440 s\u0436?! Is l\u0436ir \u0437n m\u0436id at\u0440 r\u0440ite aige nach nd\u0436anfaidh aon smaoineamh at\u0440 aige ach d\u044cobh\u0440l. (Is feidir leat an Leader\u045as Debate a fh\u0440il ar <a href=\"http://www.tg4.tv/main.aspx?level=Dios\">http://www.tg4.tv/main.aspx?level=Dios</a>). B\u044c ag smaoineamh air, a l\u0436itheoir\u044c. Is l\u0436ir do ch\u0440ch go bhfuil an \u0409plean\u045a seo lochtach, m\u044c-\u0436ifeachtach agus leisci\u0429il nach dtugann don teanga ach fadhbanna.\n\nMar sin, measaim go bhfuil s\u0436 soil\u0436ir nach n-aonta\u044cm le h\u2554anna maidir le Gaeilge agus an c\u0437ras oideachais. Ach, aonta\u044cm leis, ar phointe amh\u0440in: t\u0440 rud \u0436igin m\u0437r in easnamh sa ch\u0437ras. Mar is eol do mhadra\u044c an bhaile, is \u044c an ghn\u0436 is m\u0437 f\u0440is sa Ghaeilge n\u0440 r\u0436imse an oideachais tr\u044c Ghaeilge. Ach conas is f\u0436idir linn r\u0436iteach a fh\u0440il, conas is f\u0436idir an teanga a chur chun cinn?\n\nT\u0440 an r\u0436iteach d\u044creach \u0437s do chomhair. Gach uair a log\u0440ileann t\u0429 isteach ar facebook, gach uair at\u0440 t\u0429 ag l\u0436amh alt ar irishtimes.com, gach uair a bh\u044conn t\u0429 ag \u0429s\u0440id an idirl\u044con go ginearalta, is f\u0436idir leat a bheith ag foghlaim na teanga. Is \u0436 mo thuairimse go bhfuil s\u0436 do theist ag an rialtas an Ghaeilge a chur chun chinn go l\u0440idir- <strong>ar an idirl\u044con. </strong>\n\nIs \u044c an fh\u044crinne lom at\u0440 agam nach bhfuil an t-eolas ar f\u0440il do dhaoine faoi na su\u044comhanna idirl\u044cne as Gaeilge. Mar sin, ba bhrea liom liosta gearr a thabhairt amach faoi na su\u044comhanna gaeilge is fearr liomsa. T\u0440 na cinn seo go hiontach, m\u0440s tosaitheoir th\u0429 n\u0437 cainteoir l\u044cofa.\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">(a) Facebook</span></h3>\nA Gl\u0429ine Facebook (<em>facebook generation), </em>spreagaim d\u044cobh rud amh\u0440in a dh\u0436anamh: t\u0436igh chuig do leathanach, agus athraigh do theanga go gaeilge. Beidh t\u0429 ag smaoineamh as gaeilge I gc\u0429pla noim\u0436ad. Dra\u044cochtach.\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">(b) Abair leat</span></h3>\nC\u0429rsa tarraingteach ar an idirl\u044con \u0436 seo.T\u0440 an su\u044comh seo cabhrach do dhalta\u044c \u0437 bhunl\u0436ibh\u0436al go me\u0440nl\u0436ibh\u0436al chumais.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.lurgan.biz/art/index.htm\">http://www.lurgan.biz/art/index.htm</a>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">(c) TG4.ie</span></h3>\nCeol ar an Imeall! Seacht! GAA Beo agus n\u044cos m\u0437. TG4 player at\u0440 I gceist anseo, agus t\u0440 r\u0436imse leathan cl\u0440racha ar f\u0440il ann.\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">(d) Beo</span></h3>\nIris ar l\u044cne \u0436 Beo. Faightear l\u0436argas ar ch\u0429rsa\u044c reatha, sp\u0437irt, na heala\u044cona, c\u0429rsa\u044c teicneola\u044cochta, agus taisteal.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_2858\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"300\" caption=\"&quot;Foils\u044ctear ailt ar an su\u044comh gr\u0436as\u0440in faoi ch\u0429rsa\u044c Gaeilge, litr\u044cochta, eala\u044cne agus eile!&quot;\"]<a href=\"http://www.universitytimes.ie/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/irish-times.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-2858\" title=\"irish-times\" src=\"http://www.universitytimes.ie/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/irish-times-300x276.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"276\" /></a>[/caption]\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">(e) N\u0437s</span></h3>\nIris eile ar l\u044cne againne. D\u044crithe ar dhaoine \u0437ga, cl\u0429da\u044ctear c\u0429rsa\u044c cheoil, scann\u0440in, teilif\u044cse, teicneola\u044cochta, sp\u0437irt, c\u0429rsa\u044creatha, litr\u044cochta, taistil, agus st\u044cl agus beatha ar an su\u044comh seo.\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">(f) The Irish Times - An Teanga Bheo</span></h3>\nFoils\u044ctear ailt ar an su\u044comh gr\u0436as\u0440in faoi ch\u0429rsa\u044c Gaeilge, litr\u044cochta, eala\u044cne agus eile. T\u0440 na hailt seo oiri\u0429nach do mhic l\u0436inn \u0437 mhe\u0440nleibh\u0436al go hardleibh\u0436al chumais.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.irishtimes.com/anteangabheo/\">http://www.irishtimes.com/anteangabheo/</a>\n\nSeo c\u0429pla su\u044comhanna. Faraoir, n\u044cl m\u0437r\u0440n ann. Caithfidh an c\u0440s a fheabhs\u0429, cinnte deimhnitheach. Ba bhr\u0436a liomsa d\u0440 dtabharfadh na polaiteoir\u044c aird ar an r\u0436imse f\u0440is seo, seachas dul i gcoinne na Gaeilge sna scoileanna.\n\nT\u0440 dualgas ar an ngl\u0429in seo i leith na Gaeilge. T\u0440imid freagrach aisti. Mar sin, scaip an sc\u0436al. B\u044c ag us\u0440id su\u044comhanna as Gaeilge, agus b\u044c ag foghlaim- go n\u0440durtha, gan staid\u0436ar a dh\u0436anamh! Caithim\u044cd go l\u0436ir mionghaeltacht a chruth\u0429\u0401 in \u0440r n-aigne. Beidh tuamoideachas (<em>immersion education</em>) ar si\u0429l agat, agus n\u044c bheidh t\u0429 ag tabhairt faoi deara \u0436!\n\nTodhca\u044c ilteangach at\u0440 romhainn. Beidh dh\u0440 n\u0437 tr\u044c theanga an-\u0429s\u0440ideach as seo amach\u0401 b\u044codh an Ghaeilge mar cheann acu!", "Imageurl": "2860", "Thumb_nail": "http://universitytimes.ie/wp-content/uploads/2013/utlogo.jpg", "ID": "2855", "Heading": "An Ghaeilge agus an Idirl\u00edon - R\u00e9iteach na Faidhbe?"}